title: Beethoven - The Piano Concertos - Hogwood, AAM, Lubin
description:
Beethoven: The Piano Concertos.

Beethoven's five piano concertos, performed by Steven Lubin (fortepiano) and the Academy of Ancient Music, conducted by Christopher Hogwood. This three disc set was released by L'Oiseau-Lyre in 1988. The concertos are magnificently performed and recorded, with Lubin playing different fortepianos--contemporary to the time of composition--for each concerto.

Please enjoy.
